    <stitle>AIR COMPRESSOR: BENDIX 2150 - CLEANING - OIL PASSAGES</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="clean" graphiccount="0">
        <title>OIL PASSAGES</title>
        <para>Thoroughly clean all oil passages through the crankshaft, crankcase, end covers, and base plate or base
            adapter. Inspect the passages with a wire to be sure they are clear. Blow the loosened foreign matter out
            with shop air.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
